CBRE as exclusive agents are pleased to present For Sale Units 3 and 4, 5 Stretton Place, Balcatta. Strategically located within the highly regarded industrial precinct of Balcatta, this quality office/warehouse facility provides a versatile acquisition opportunity within a tightly held location.

Property Features:
- Blue-chip city fringe commercial/ industrial location
- Proximity to Balcatta and Erindale Roads
- Good access to key transportation routes including Mitchell Freeway and Reid Highway
- Office: 393sqm*
- Lab: 43sqm*
- Warehouse: 452sqm* 
- Roller door access
- High truss warehouse
- Zoned “Industry” 
- Exclusive parking
- Strata Area 762sqm*

For further details please contact the exclusive selling agents.

The property is offered for sale via Request for Offers campaign closing Monday the 26th of July 2022 at 3pm AEST.

*approx

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
24 Geddes Street features a well-appointed freestanding single level office situated on an 8,195sqm site located within the highly sought after commercial/industrial precinct of Balcatta.  Join Brownes Dairy, Balcatta HQ and Campbells Wholesalers in this strategically located precinct with Stirling Central Shopping Centre situated on nearby Wanneroo Road.  The property has a Gross Lettable Area of 2,100sqm* and Net Lettable Area of 1,995sqm*.

KEY FEATURES:
•	Building Area 2,100sqm* (GLA) 
•	Site Area: 8,195 sqm*
•	Proximity to the Mitchell Freeway, Reid Highway and Wanneroo Road
•	75 Parking Bays (including 2 x Disabled Bays)
•	Close to established amenity including Stirling Central Shopping Centre
•	Zoned “Industry” under the City of Stirling’s TPS 3
•	Vacant possession at settlement 
•	12km* to Perth CBD
•	Neighbours include Brownes Diary, Balcatta HQ and Campbells Wholesalers
•	Auditorium with 35+ Person Capacity
•	2-Star NABERS energy rating

Offers Invited Close 3pm AWST Thursday 20th June 2019.  For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive sales agents.

*Approx
